{"id":9,"date":"2009-02-11T15:07:36","date_gmt":"2009-02-11T15:07:36","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.ac.uk\/vl_blog\/?page_id=9"},"modified":"2015-02-03T12:31:32","modified_gmt":"2015-02-03T12:31:32","slug":"expensiveware","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/?page_id=9","title":{"rendered":"Software for Visual Learning"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2009\/02\/conceptmaps.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-497\" title=\"Concept Maps\" src=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2009\/02\/conceptmaps-300x210.jpg\" alt=\"Concept Maps\" width=\"300\" height=\"210\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2009\/02\/conceptmaps-300x210.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2009\/02\/conceptmaps.jpg 777w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Most software can be used to support Visual Learning &#8211; all of the packages that come with Interactive Whiteboards, for example, not to mention elements of the various Office packages.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2009\/02\/visual-learning-software.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-527\" title=\"visual-learning-software\" src=\"http:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2009\/02\/visual-learning-software-300x290.jpg\" alt=\"visual-learning-software\" width=\"300\" height=\"290\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2009\/02\/visual-learning-software-300x290.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.mirandanet.org.uk\/vl_blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2009\/02\/visual-learning-software.jpg 684w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/a>This map of Visual Learning software was produced with <a href=\"htt